 <body>
  <p> This sentence should be green. </p>
  <p class="a"> This sentence <span class="a1">should be</span> white on green. </p>
  <p class="b"> <em>PASS</em> <strong>FAIL</strong> </p>
  <p class="c"> PASS <dfn>FAIL</dfn> </p>
